summary: Technical Physician (MSc. Technical Medicine Sensing & Stimulation) seeking to be the hybrid between medicine and engineering. Integrating a problem-solving approach with creative thinking, medical knowledge and engineering skills to innovate and safely implement improved diagnostics and multimodal monitoring. Passionate about paediatrics, cardiology and computer science.
